item.description:
JadenHsiao https://www.jytype.cn/php/yii/yii2-skills-part-six/ -<blockquote>
<p>在业务开发中，对于用户上传的文件需要进行安全校验，<em>Yii</em>本身提供了<em>FileValidator</em>的文件校验类；但是文件校验类对于word、excel、powerpoint的校验只是针对Microsoft，而wps的文件格式并不支持，因此需要重写文件校验类来达到我们的需求。</p>
</blockquote>
<p>通过断点调试，得知<em>FileValidator</em>是通过获取上传文件的<em>MimeType</em>和后缀，然后将后置通过<em>yiisoft/yii2/helpers/mimeTypes.php</em>中返回的数组获取到对应<em>Yii</em>设定的<em>MimeType</em>，对比是否一致，如果不一致则抛出校验错误。</p>
<h2 id="一重写上传校验类">一、重写上传校验类</h2>
<p>因此重写的思路就是在<em>Yii</em>进行系统判断前，我们新增WPS特殊的格式的校验，如果命中就直接返回验证通过，代码如下：</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-php" data-lang="php"><span style="display:flex;"><span>&lt;?php
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">namespace</span> app\validators;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">use</span> yii\validators\FileValidator <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">as</span> Base;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">use</span> yii\helpers\FileHelper;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">class</span> <span style="color:#008b45;font-weight:bold">FileValidator</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">extends</span> Base
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>{
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">protected</span> <span style="color:#00688b">$extra</span> = [
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;docx&#34;</span> =&gt; <span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;application/zip&#34;</span>,
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;et&#34;</span> =&gt; <span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;application/vnd.ms-excel&#34;</span>,
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;xlsx&#34;</span> =&gt; <span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;application/zip&#34;</span>,
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;ett&#34;</span> =&gt; <span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;application/vnd.ms-excel&#34;</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    ];
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">protected</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">function</span> <span style="color:#008b45">validateExtension</span>(<span style="color:#00688b">$file</span>)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#00688b">$extension</span> = mb_strtolower(<span style="color:#00688b">$file</span>-&gt;<span style="color:#658b00">extension</span>, <span style="color:#cd5555">&#39;UTF-8&#39;</span>);
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span> (<span style="color:#00688b">$this</span>-&gt;<span style="color:#658b00">checkExtensionByMimeType</span>) {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            <span style="color:#00688b">$mimeType</span> = FileHelper::<span style="color:#658b00">getMimeType</span>(<span style="color:#00688b">$file</span>-&gt;<span style="color:#658b00">tempName</span>, <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">null</span>, <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">false</span>);
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span> (<span style="color:#00688b">$mimeType</span> === <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">null</span>) {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>                <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">false</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            <span style="color:#00688b">$extensionsByMimeType</span> = FileHelper::<span style="color:#658b00">getExtensionsByMimeType</span>(<span style="color:#00688b">$mimeType</span>);
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span>(<span style="color:#00688b">$this</span>-&gt;<span style="color:#658b00">extra</span>[<span style="color:#00688b">$extension</span>] == <span style="color:#00688b">$mimeType</span>){
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>                <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">true</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span> (!in_array(<span style="color:#00688b">$extension</span>, <span style="color:#00688b">$extensionsByMimeType</span>, <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">true</span>)) {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>                <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">false</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span> (!in_array(<span style="color:#00688b">$extension</span>, <span style="color:#00688b">$this</span>-&gt;<span style="color:#658b00">extensions</span>, <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">true</span>)) {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">false</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">true</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>}
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>上面的代码块中，<code>$extra</code>是我们对于WPS的文件设定的额外校验规则，在方法<code>validateExtension</code>中，判断后缀名和<em>MimeType</em>是否一致是的话就放行。</p>
<h2 id="二表单模型中调用">二、表单模型中调用</h2>
<p>在调用时要引用我们重写的工具类，在表单校验规则中指定为<code>FileValidator::className()</code>，而不是原先的<code>file</code>；</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-php" data-lang="php"><span style="display:flex;"><span>&lt;?php
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">use</span> yii\base\Model;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">use</span> yii\helper\ArrayHelper;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">use</span> app\validators\FileValidator;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">class</span> <span style="color:#008b45;font-weight:bold">Example</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">extends</span> Model{
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">public</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">function</span> <span style="color:#008b45">rules</span>()
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#00688b">$parent_rules</span> = <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">parent</span>::<span style="color:#658b00">rules</span>(); <span style="color:#228b22">// TODO: Change the autogenerated stub
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#228b22"></span>    
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#00688b">$rules</span> = [
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            [
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>                <span style="color:#cd5555">&#39;files&#39;</span>,
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>                FileValidator::<span style="color:#658b00">className</span>(),
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>                <span style="color:#cd5555">&#39;skipOnEmpty&#39;</span> =&gt; <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">false</span>,
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>                <span style="color:#cd5555">&#39;extensions&#39;</span> =&gt; <span style="color:#cd5555">&#39;png,jpg,jpeg,gif,doc,dot,docx,xls,xlt,xlsx,xlsm,ppt,pot,pps,pptx,pdf&#39;</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            ],
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        ];
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> ArrayHelper::<span style="color:#658b00">merge</span>(
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            <span style="color:#00688b">$parent_rules</span>,
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            <span style="color:#00688b">$rules</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        );
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>}
</span></span></code></pre></div>- https://www.jytype.cn/php/yii/yii2-skills-part-six/ - Jadenhsiao. 本站遵循 CC-BY-NC 4.0 协议

JadenHsiao https://www.jytype.cn/leetcode/algorithms/two-sum/ -<p>给定一个整数数组 nums 和一个目标值 target，请你在该数组中找出和为目标值的那 两个 整数，并返回他们的数组下标。</p>
<p>你可以假设每种输入只会对应一个答案。但是，数组中同一个元素不能使用两遍。</p>
<blockquote>
<p>示例:</p>
<p>给定 nums = [2, 7, 11, 15], target = 9 因为 nums[0] + nums[1] = 2 + 7 = 9
所以返回 [0, 1]</p>
</blockquote>
<p>代码内容：</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-php" data-lang="php"><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">class</span> <span style="color:#008b45;font-weight:bold">Solution</span> {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#cd5555">/**
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#cd5555">     * @param Integer[] $nums
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#cd5555">     * @param Integer $target
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#cd5555">     * @return Integer[]
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#cd5555">     */</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">function</span> <span style="color:#008b45">twoSum</span>(<span style="color:#00688b">$nums</span>, <span style="color:#00688b">$target</span>) {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#00688b">$res</span> = [];
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">for</span>(<span style="color:#00688b">$i</span> = <span style="color:#b452cd">0</span>;<span style="color:#00688b">$i</span> &lt; count(<span style="color:#00688b">$nums</span>);<span style="color:#00688b">$i</span>++){
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">foreach</span>(<span style="color:#00688b">$nums</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">as</span> <span style="color:#00688b">$item</span>=&gt;<span style="color:#00688b">$value</span>){
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>                <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span>(<span style="color:#00688b">$nums</span>[<span style="color:#00688b">$i</span>] + <span style="color:#00688b">$nums</span>[<span style="color:#00688b">$item</span>] == <span style="color:#00688b">$target</span> &amp;&amp; <span style="color:#00688b">$i</span>!=<span style="color:#00688b">$item</span>){
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>                        <span style="color:#00688b">$temp</span>[] = <span style="color:#00688b">$i</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>                        <span style="color:#00688b">$temp</span>[] = <span style="color:#00688b">$item</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>                        sort(<span style="color:#00688b">$temp</span>);
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>                        <span style="color:#00688b">$res</span>[] = <span style="color:#00688b">$temp</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            <span style="color:#00688b">$temp</span> = [];
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>                }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#00688b">$res</span> = array_unique(<span style="color:#00688b">$res</span>, SORT_REGULAR);
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span>(count(<span style="color:#00688b">$res</span>)==<span style="color:#b452cd">1</span>){
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> <span style="color:#00688b">$res</span>[<span style="color:#b452cd">0</span>];
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    }
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>思路：题目要求是在一个给定数组内找出两个相加为给定值，因此将该给定的数组进行遍历后再遍历，遍历时两个值是不能相等的，同时相加的结果为给定的值，遍历出来后会出现下标是一样的情况但是位置不同，所以要对结果进行去重，确保可以去重得先对每一次获得的结果进行升序，再进行去重就可以得到最终的结果。</p>
- https://www.jytype.cn/leetcode/algorithms/two-sum/ - Jadenhsiao. 本站遵循 CC-BY-NC 4.0 协议

JadenHsiao https://www.jytype.cn/leetcode/algorithms/search-insert-position/ -<p>给定一个排序数组和一个目标值，在数组中找到目标值，并返回其索引。如果目标值不存在于数组中，返回它将会被按顺序插入的位置。</p>
<p>你可以假设数组中无重复元素。</p>
<blockquote>
<p>示例 1:</p>
<p>输入: [1,3,5,6], 5 输出: 2</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>示例 2:</p>
<p>输入: [1,3,5,6], 7 输出: 4</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>示例 3:</p>
<p>输入: [0,3,5,6], 0 输出: 0</p>
</blockquote>
<p>代码内容：</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-php" data-lang="php"><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">class</span> <span style="color:#008b45;font-weight:bold">Solution</span> {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#cd5555">/**
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#cd5555">     * @param Integer[] $nums
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#cd5555">     * @param Integer $target
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#cd5555">     * @return Integer
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#cd5555">     */</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">function</span> <span style="color:#008b45">searchInsert</span>(<span style="color:#00688b">$nums</span>, <span style="color:#00688b">$target</span>) {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span>(in_array(<span style="color:#00688b">$target</span>,<span style="color:#00688b">$nums</span>)){
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            <span style="color:#00688b">$result</span> = array_search(<span style="color:#00688b">$target</span>,<span style="color:#00688b">$nums</span>);
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> <span style="color:#00688b">$result</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        }<span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">else</span>{
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span>(min(<span style="color:#00688b">$nums</span>)&gt;<span style="color:#00688b">$target</span>){
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>                <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> <span style="color:#b452cd">0</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span>(max(<span style="color:#00688b">$nums</span>)&lt;<span style="color:#00688b">$target</span>){
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>                <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> count(<span style="color:#00688b">$nums</span>);
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">for</span>(<span style="color:#00688b">$i</span>=<span style="color:#b452cd">0</span>;<span style="color:#00688b">$i</span>&lt;count(<span style="color:#00688b">$nums</span>);<span style="color:#00688b">$i</span>++){
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>                <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span>(<span style="color:#00688b">$nums</span>[<span style="color:#00688b">$i</span>]&lt;<span style="color:#00688b">$target</span> &amp;&amp; <span style="color:#00688b">$nums</span>[<span style="color:#00688b">$i</span>+<span style="color:#b452cd">1</span>]&gt;<span style="color:#00688b">$target</span>){
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>                    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> <span style="color:#00688b">$i</span>+<span style="color:#b452cd">1</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>                }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    }
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>思路：本题主要是位置查找问题，如果在数组内就返回对应的下标，比最小值的小就返回第一个值的下标，比最大值的大就返回最大值插入的位置，否则就返回插入的位置，因此，先跟最小的比较，再跟最大的比较，如果都不成立就走遍历，从遍历里当前的和往前一位的比较，如果在中间就直接取前一位的位置。</p>
- https://www.jytype.cn/leetcode/algorithms/search-insert-position/ - Jadenhsiao. 本站遵循 CC-BY-NC 4.0 协议

JadenHsiao https://www.jytype.cn/leetcode/algorithms/reverse-integer/ -<p>给出一个 32 位的有符号整数，你需要将这个整数中每位上的数字进行反转。</p>
<blockquote>
<p>示例 1:</p>
<p>输入: 123 输出: 321</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>示例 2:</p>
<p>输入: -123 输出: -321</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>示例 3:</p>
<p>输入: 120 输出: 21</p>
</blockquote>
<p>注意:</p>
<p>假设我们的环境只能存储得下 32 位的有符号整数，则其数值范围为 [−231,  231 − 1]。请根据这个假设，如果反转后整数溢出那么就返回 0。
代码内容：</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-php" data-lang="php"><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">class</span> <span style="color:#008b45;font-weight:bold">Solution</span> {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#cd5555">/**
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#cd5555">     * @param Integer $x
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#cd5555">     * @return Integer
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#cd5555">     */</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">function</span> <span style="color:#008b45">reverse</span>(<span style="color:#00688b">$x</span>) {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#00688b">$b</span> = <span style="color:#00688b">$x</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span>(<span style="color:#00688b">$x</span>&lt;<span style="color:#b452cd">0</span>){
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            <span style="color:#00688b">$x</span> = <span style="color:#00688b">$x</span>*-<span style="color:#b452cd">1</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span>(<span style="color:#00688b">$b</span> == <span style="color:#b452cd">0</span>){
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> <span style="color:#00688b">$b</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#00688b">$result</span> = implode(array_reverse(str_split(<span style="color:#00688b">$x</span>)));
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#00688b">$t</span> = trim(<span style="color:#00688b">$result</span>,<span style="color:#b452cd">0</span>);
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span>(<span style="color:#00688b">$t</span>&gt;pow(<span style="color:#b452cd">2</span>,<span style="color:#b452cd">31</span>)){
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>                <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> <span style="color:#b452cd">0</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> <span style="color:#00688b">$b</span>&lt;<span style="color:#b452cd">0</span>?<span style="color:#00688b">$t</span>*-<span style="color:#b452cd">1</span>:<span style="color:#00688b">$t</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    }
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>思路：如果提供的值小于0，就转化为正数再进行转化为数组，翻转再成为数组，同时去掉前面的0和判断是否大于2的31次方，对应情况就是如果为小于0就返回为翻转后小于0的数，如果大于2的31次方就返回0。</p>
